{"tid":1613879,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上半年18警欠稅21.3萬元 欠稅額相當去年全年九成","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:56:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c550a760cf85f246b8295cd53f7a084939071b14","tid":1613879,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"保安局向立法會提交最新資料，今年上半年總計有18名警員遭追討稅款，總計涉拖欠稅款約21.3萬元，以拖欠金額計，數字達去年全年近9成。當局又指出，截至今年6月30日，警隊中共有27名警員無力還債，其中1人屬新個案，亦有個案已遭債務糾纏近14年。<br />\n<br />\n保安局文件指出，今年上半年遭追討稅款的警員人數為18人，雖然個案數字低於去年的同期的27宗，亦較2017年上半年42宗的高峯期有所回落。但以欠稅金額計算，今年上半年18名欠稅警員共拖欠21.3萬元，去年全年全數31宗個案，則合共欠稅24.3萬元；今年上半年的警員欠稅總額，已達去年全年近9成"},{"pid":"424f840d42eb4aa7d14be678c724201a28a40df0","tid":1613879,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191002/60110195?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60110195%3F&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX2dKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=f769805f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60110195%3F&h=23bdf6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191002/60110195?</a>"},{"pid":"63dd99ee4e30f3dc18f76b576fb422502d86d3ad","tid":1613879,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"知法犯法, 罰三倍penalty la"}]}